OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FChilly
OL,6,Fstart Friday then sunny intervals,
OL,7,Fcloud thickening later. Rain and
OL,8,Fstrong winds early Saturday, followed
OL,9,Fby sunshine and blustery showers into
OL,10,FSunday. Feeling rather cool at times.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
